### Weather Image Generator API Documentation
### Deployed Azure Function App (Publicly Accessible - No Authentication Required)

@functionAppUrl = https://weatherimg693430-func.azurewebsites.net

### 1. Start a new image generation job
POST {{functionAppUrl}}/api/jobs
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 2. Get job status (replace {jobId} with actual job ID from step 1)
GET {{functionAppUrl}}/api/jobs/f5797284-af59-449e-9328-d059753ac6ca

###

### Example: Complete workflow
